title: Seattle RB Fred Jackson uninjured in car crash
text:
> Sports Seattle RB Fred Jackson uninjured in car crash This photo provided by Curtis Crabtree shows tire tracks in the dirt near the sign for the Seattle Seahawks NFL football headquarters after a car driven by Seahawks running back Fred Jackson crashed near the sign Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, in Renton, Wash. Jackson was uninjured. (Curtis Crabtree via AP)
